        Parametric constructor
        Parameters:
        srNo - Unique ID (int value) for this event.
        eventID - Specific number for this event. May be duplicate.
        guestCount - Count of the guest in this event.
        startTime - Start time of this event. 24 hr format.
        endTime - End time of this event. 24 hr format.
        eventName - Name of this event (if any)
        eventLocation - Location/Venue of this event.
        day - Day of the week for this event.
        isDisposable - Service type of this event: Disposable or China.
        date - Date on which this event is supposed to happen.
